description: If I attacked you first, thanks for the EXP and Coins, I hope we can be freinds in the future! If you attacked me first, congratulations! You tried! If you have a rude death message, WE WISH YOU WERE NEVER BORN. Anyway I hope you have a good day.
about: I used my moms Email because I don't have one so it instead shows June 8 as the caaaake day. I change my username often. I usually like to have a territory above tier 8. I am a perfectionist. What that means is that whenever I die in this game I restart.
